messages.title: Please update the app
messages.content:
You're running an old version of Xpotify, which is now experiencing issues.
Please update the app to continue using it.

To update, open Microsoft Store, go to 'Downloads and updates' from the ... menu on the top right corner, and click on 'Check for updates'.
Note that Xpotify is recently renamed to Xpo Music, and you will see the new name after updating the app.
